# interview-prep-kit needs NO secrets to run — the kit is markdown skills + hooks.
# This file exists so the secret-scan hook's `.env` guard has a safe, committable counterpart.
# If you wire in an optional API (e.g. to fetch a company's public site), put its key in a real
# `.env` (which is gitignored) and document it here.

# EXAMPLE_FETCH_API_KEY="your-key-here"
